                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">About us</h1>
                <p class="display-6 fw-bold text-secondary">Welcome To EduVenture Mubarak<br/>Empowering Africa's Future Leaders</p>
                <p>we believe that every child, no matter where they come from, deserves the right to quality education. Founded with a vision to address illiteracy among children under 16 in rural Africa, starting from Egypt, our mission is to revolutionize education delivery through innovative and accessible solutions.</p>
                <p>We aim to close the education gap by providing both **traditional** and **digital** educational content, tailored to meet the needs of children in underprivileged communities. Our content spans from basic literacy and numeracy to advanced subjects like science, technology, and genetics, all crafted to foster a deep love for learning in students.</p>
                <p>Our **Caravan Project** brings learning to the doorstep of rural communities, offering lessons through **physical books** and **digital platforms**. We utilize projectors and mobile technology to make learning materials accessible even in areas with limited infrastructure.</p>
